  A few days ago HOODLUM released their GTA: San Andreas. But on some systems it
  doesn't work properly, caused by some crappy Windows mistakes. To get it work,
  you need to create a new Windows account OR change something in the EXE. So
  this fix is for guys, who don't get the time to fix this shit. This is a fix
  done with the guide from

  http://www.gtaforums.com/index.php?showtopic=194371

  Thanks goes out to mustrum (DFXP) who found the crappy mistake in Windows and
  to HOODLUM for their really fine release we used the crack from to fix it.



